claim.claim-text:
An electrochemical cell, comprising:
a first cell comprising a first power generation element and a first inner container, the first inner container accommodating the first power generation element, and a surface of the first inner container being provided with a convexity that has a curved surface and/or a flat surface;
a second cell comprising a second power generation element and a second inner container, the second inner container accommodating the second power generation element, and a surface of the second inner container being provided with a concavity that has a curved surface and/or a flat surface;
an outer container which accommodates the first cell and the second cell; and
a fit portion in which the convexity is fitted in the concavity.

An electrochemical cell module, comprising:
a housing;
a first electrochemical cell according to any one of claims 1 to 10, the first electrochemical cell being located inside the housing;
a second electrochemical cell according to any one of claims 1 to 10, the second electrochemical cell being located inside the housing; and
a connection portion that electrically connects the first electrochemical cell and the second electrochemical cell.
